		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Iguanicus&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>I am a Shadow Knight and I feel that it is pointless to use your pets. Save your mana for Spells. I would suggest using Siphon Strength spell to pull your enemies and If your solo use a good combination of DOTs and Sapping Spells. Since you are a tank I think that you do not need a pet cause you can wear heavy armor and take alot of hits.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>I am Iguanicus TheLizard of Tunare Server</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >4 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
